# E-Cartz - E-Commerce Platform

## Overview
E-Cartz is a simple e-commerce platform built with **React**, **Bootstrap**, and **Tailwind CSS** on the frontend, while the backend is powered by **Node.js**, **Express.js**, and **MongoDB**. The platform enables users to register, log in, and view products. Admins have exclusive privileges to add new products.

## Live Links
- **Frontend Live:** [E-Cartz Frontend](https://e-cartzz-jishan-task.netlify.app/)
- **Backend Live:** [E-Cartz Backend](https://ecartz-backend.onrender.com/)

## Features
### User Features
- **User Registration & Login** (JWT-based authentication)
- **View available products** with detailed descriptions
- **Fully responsive design** for all screen sizes

### Admin Features
- **Admin Login** (Email: `admin@gmail.com`, Password: `admin123`)
- **Add new products** with details including:
  - Product Name
  - Price
  - Brand
  - Available Stock
  - Description
  - Product Image (via Multer for handling `multipart/form-data` uploads)
- **Admin Dashboard** for product management
- **Redirection to Admin Panel** upon successful admin login

## Tech Stack
### Frontend:
- **React.js** - Component-based UI development
- **Bootstrap** - Styling and responsiveness
- **Tailwind CSS** - Utility-first styling

### Backend:
- **Node.js** - Runtime environment
- **Express.js** - Backend framework
- **MongoDB & Mongoose** - Database and ORM
- **JWT (JSON Web Token)** - Authentication & Authorization
- **Multer Middleware** - Handling image uploads

